    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Fair-condition car that looks decent from a distance but shows clear signs of age and use up close. The body and paint have visible cosmetic wear, and buyers should expect blemishes, imperfections, and general aging throughout. The interior is serviceable but not especially fresh, with normal wear from use. This is best suited for someone looking for an affordable driver or a vehicle to improve over time rather than a pristine example.",
