    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Clean, honest driver in fair overall condition with good value for someone looking for an affordable, usable car. It shows visible cosmetic wear and normal age-related imperfections, but it still presents decently and has plenty of life left for its next owner. A solid choice if you want something enjoyable and budget-friendly without expecting a perfect example.",
