      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "$46,900 - Truly mint condition and the kind of car that stands out immediately. It presents exceptionally well throughout, with outstanding paint, trim, interior, and overall finish, showing the careful ownership and preservation buyers hope to find but rarely do. The cabin is clean, crisp, and very well kept, and the exterior has the deep, well-maintained appearance of a car that has been properly cared for rather than simply cleaned up for sale. This is not an average used example\u2014it\u2019s a top-tier car for someone who wants an especially sharp, well-preserved vehicle they can be proud to own.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Dependable transportation at an accessible price, this vehicle is a practical choice for buyers who value affordability and everyday utility. It shows its age and is best suited for someone seeking a straightforward car with solid potential as a commuter, first vehicle, or backup. Represented with honesty and priced to deliver clear value, this is a smart opportunity to get on the road without overspending.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car that\u2019s ready for someone who wants affordable wheels or a good little project. It\u2019s not perfect, but it has plenty of life left for the right buyer and could make a great runaround, first car, or handy backup vehicle. Priced fairly for what it is, and I\u2019m happy to be straightforward about it \u2014 if you\u2019re after honest value without spending a fortune, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with good bones and plenty of upside for the next owner. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it a great budget commuter, shop truck, or weekend project. Cosmetically it shows its age and will want attention, but the core package is there: dependable starting, usable torque, and a platform that still has life left in it. If you want an affordable driver you can improve as you go, this one makes a compelling case.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    }
  ],
